A wealthy elderly couple have been found murdered in their luxury LA home.

The pair have been named as Shirley Isom, 74, and Armie Troy Isom, 89 - they lived in a home north of La Verne.

Mrs Isom died at the couple’s home, while Mr Isom was taken to hospital but died. 

