Los Angeles County Sheriff's Department Lt. Dave Coleman said the couple died from blunt trauma.

Police initially reported that the couple were killed in a stabbing - is understood the confusion arose because there was a lot of blood at the scene.

Their bodies were found near the front door of their home by their groundskeeper.

