Police are now searching for a man who was seen running from the property. 

The Sheriff's Department later said that no suspect information was available.

Neighbor Lorrie Guzzy told KTLA said the man she saw leaving the Isoms' home was wearing a backpack and looked 'homeless' and suspicious. 

'It's a shock,' neighbor and friend Don Mineer said. 

